html
  include includes/head.pug
  head
  body
    .position-relative.overflow-hidden.p-3.text-center.bg-light
      .col-md-5.p-lg-5.mx-auto.my-5
        h2.display-5.fw-normal Available properties
        strong=authorised
        p.lead.fw-normal
        | Here you can acquire a property, or a part of it.
  .container.px-4.py-5
    .card.mb-5
      h5.card-header=tokens1
      .card-body
        form(method='get' action='buy')
          h5.card-title Utrecht 1
          p.card-text Available percentage: #{balance1}
          input.form-control.w-25.mt-4(type='hidden' name='token' value='#{balance1}' placeholder='Percentage (10%)')
          input.form-control.w-25.mt-4(type='text' name='percentage' placeholder='Percentage (10%)')
          input.btn.btn-primary.mt-4(type='submit' value='Acquire')
